":"1d3503c9ca8d396d6c8f6ad9c52ea7c4a12f3698","tid":131914,"uid":67696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人出過聚，多mk？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地都幾多車聚，真係鐘意聚咪入下谷玩下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d9d22dcb184a2e2e33483d60edf295bbbdfb29","tid":131914,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"已填form但唔係90後，差少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad731e965c447ea8496e60377d284b250b6442a","tid":131914,"uid":46512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個group全部都係歐洲車、跑車、MK車，<br />\n如果唔係揸上述車，可以唔使入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmk車？</blockquote><br />\n我地個群其實除左歐洲車、跑車、MK車<br />\n仲有日本車、原裝車、家庭車、經典車、電單車等等<br />\n車款有重改有原裝、有NA有Turbo、有電油有純電、有新有舊、有兩座有七座<br />\n巴打有興趣既可以入黎出下車聚 始終眼見為實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5079075b18eda4253e471981e8bd5ed87ac6b59e","tid":131914,"uid":46512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果閣下你唔係渣跑車、歐洲車 <br />\n真係唔建議入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有<br />\n如果閣下冇汽車知識，唔識埋堆，唔鐘意出聚<br />\n真係咪撚入</blockquote><br />\n如果唔出聚又真係唔知入嚟做咩喎<br />\n利申無入</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔係既, 我有同部分冇出過聲既巴打私下傾過下<br />\n其實都唔少人係鍾意齋睇唔參與, 其實我對此冇咩意見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過個谷Full左又有新巴打想入個陣我就可能會問下呢類巴打意願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"590650d96a3d7385b19268406e0468ce43ef3355","tid":131914,"uid":46512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想入但谷友揸啲咩多？揸錢七only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩車都有，咩人都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心, 唔洗怕你部車唔夠靚, 我都只係渣部5000蚊買入既錢柒<br />\n人人背景唔同負擔能力唔同, 我渣爛車但我自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449ab7e67b80fa19778b30a228d4f23ac1b7ebd5","tid":131914,"uid":67696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想入但谷友揸啲咩多？揸錢七only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩車都有，咩人都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心, 唔洗怕你部車唔夠靚, 我都只係渣部5000蚊買入既錢柒<br />\n人人背景唔同負擔能力唔同, 我渣爛車但我自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成部車都係曱甴"},{"pid":"b932fbb27f19d22a706913993cf476d3d5f0e630","tid":131914,"uid":3057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:25:03.000Z","msg":"岩岩填左表等入群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}